26:56.538 --> 26:59.773
LAWRENCE (narrating): <i>There
are five steps to any good con.</i>

26:59.775 --> 27:01.841
<i>First is roping the sucker.</i>

27:01.843 --> 27:04.147
(laughs)

27:05.214 --> 27:08.815
<i>We'd have a drink, sit
around for a bit, then leave.</i>

27:08.817 --> 27:11.217
Could you quit the Hamlet routine?

27:11.219 --> 27:13.052
What?

27:13.054 --> 27:16.290
<i>The next day, I would
