27:16.292 --> 27:19.526
Hello, my good lady.

27:19.528 --> 27:21.161
- Hi.
- Hi.

27:21.163 --> 27:22.830
- My intended and I...
- My fiancée and I...

27:22.832 --> 27:25.166
