- Wondering if you found it?

27:32.374 --> 27:34.841
- No.
- It's really special to us.

27:34.843 --> 27:37.011
- Family heirloom.
- It really means a lot to me.

27:37.013 --> 27:40.880
- So if anyone finds it...
- could you ask them to call this number?

27:40.882 --> 27:44.452
We're willing to offer you a $1,000 reward.

27:46.922 --> 27:49.023
LAWRENCE (narrating): <i>Some time
later, the Professor would arrive.</i>

27:49.025 --> 27:51.861
(laughing)

27:53.361 --> 27:57.164
<i>His favorite routine was
to pretend to be drunk.</i>

27:57.166 --> 28:00.135
- (groans)
- (grunts)

28:03.573 --> 28:06.840
- Ooh.
- Look what I found.

28:06.842 --> 28:10.343
Fuck me.

28:10.345 --> 28:13.513
- That's mine.
- Oh, finders keepers.

28:13.515 --> 28:16.216
It's worth a pretty penny, I'd wager.

28:16.218 --> 28:19.019
Mmm. (chuckles)

28:19.021 --> 28:20.553
- Fifty bucks.
- A hundred?

28:20.555 --> 28:22.555
Looks like gold to me.

28:22.557 --> 28:24.358
200. That's it.

28:24.360 --> 28:27.061
I think I'll just hang on to it.

28:27.063 --> 28:28.329
- 250.
- 300.

28:28.331 --> 28:30.765
- 375.
- 400.

28:33.134 --> 28:35.837
And a six-pack.

28:37.239 --> 28:39.173
LAWRENCE (narrating): <i>The
most money we ever made was...</i>

28:39.175 --> 28:40.976
(cash register dings)

28:45.547 --> 28:47.513
550.

28:47.515 --> 28:50.686
Hand it over, codger.

28:52.220 --> 28:54.256
(groans)

