34:48.811 --> 34:50.610
We could have been brothers.

34:50.612 --> 34:52.879
He taught me how to play cards.

34:52.880 --> 34:56.514
- He was a confidence man?
- He was no con man.

34:56.516 --> 34:58.352
He was a thief.

34:58.354 --> 35:00.586
